  "2137760": {
    "name": "Crafty Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 2137760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/8dc542981144d1ce2bc81542cce24264.poster.avif?t=1755872186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/8dc542981144d1ce2bc81542cce24264.webm?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/8dc542981144d1ce2bc81542cce24264.mp4?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特构筑层出不穷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在这款动作Roguelite游戏中，根据每次游戏的角色来选择千式百样的升级选项，打造独一无二的角色构筑。想成为大厨打一场“甜品大战”、焗烤敌人吗？还是用针线球作为武器，把敌人统统缝在一起赶尽杀绝的裁缝？你要用何种材料来雕刻你的雕像呢——木头，还是大理石？运用你的工匠才艺，寻求生存之道吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/78de9d72d297c9c62d5c5751f2448ab3.poster.avif?t=1755872186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/78de9d72d297c9c62d5c5751f2448ab3.webm?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/78de9d72d297c9c62d5c5751f2448ab3.mp4?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择工匠保卫家园</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从众多工匠与手艺人中挑选一位，每一位都有自己的独特技能与玩法机制。无论是烹饪调味并用敌人下菜、还是穿针引线把敌人缝在一起、或是打造雕像一举击垮敌人，你总能运用自己的工匠才艺捍卫家园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/6853fe78e7234d7627505a6767a1c610.poster.avif?t=1755872186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/6853fe78e7234d7627505a6767a1c610.webm?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/6853fe78e7234d7627505a6767a1c610.mp4?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级村落愈战愈勇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 击败敌人，从他们身上收集材料。用这些资源升级你的村落，解锁新角色、额外增益，助你变得更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/d780ccf5c2715f228c22adabbff5a656.poster.avif?t=1755872186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/d780ccf5c2715f228c22adabbff5a656.webm?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/d780ccf5c2715f228c22adabbff5a656.mp4?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游玩风格自己做主</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你可以自由选择技能是手动释放还是自动施法！根据不同的游戏模式，寻找最适合自己游玩风格的组合搭配！全自动，全手动，亦或是二者兼求？全都由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/16d45621f97aba73c56df3aaaf9ae476.poster.avif?t=1755872186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/16d45621f97aba73c56df3aaaf9ae476.webm?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137760/extras/16d45621f97aba73c56df3aaaf9ae476.mp4?t=1755872186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与<strong>各式各样的生物群落</strong>交手，每种都具有其独特挑战，正在持续更新中；  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >形形色色的<strong>工匠与手艺人</strong>任玩家挑选，随着更新还会有更多新面孔加入；  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都拥有<strong>独特技能树</strong>，超过<strong>上百种技能</strong>供你探索；  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为忙碌的玩家们准备的<strong>快速游戏模式</strong>；  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物系统能让你拥有能进一步自定义的<strong>独特游戏体验</strong>；  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >锻造和编织系统引入了超过80种全新被动技能，助你打造各个角色的独特游玩风格。  </p></li></ul>",
